{"tid":1630490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際戰線，美國女記者Suzanne Sataline比魔警將她包圍，嘗試制服她","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:25:03.000Z","uid":179775,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6af4efb0e793a0cda4267b70b4504d6c5b791a","tid":1630490,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"此外，防暴警又突然推撞戴綠色頭盔、穿反光衣的外媒女記者Suzanne Sataline，並將她包圍，嘗試制服她，但其後又釋放該名記者，未有解釋原因。Suzanne向記者表示，她在警方推進時跌倒，繼而有女示威者亦倒在她眼前，故她以電話繼續拍攝，惟遭警方不斷大叫「where are you from？」然而即使她多次回答來自美國，警方仍繼續追問，警方一時叫她離開、一時叫她坐下，令她感到無助，亦擔心其翻譯被捕；其間亦被警棍打到手部。<br />\n<br />\n幫Suzanne翻譯的劉先生指，Suzanne年屆56歲，在港採訪多年，剛才被警方推撞跌倒，被圍困時亦有警員朝她頭盔打一下。及後他被趕至10米範圍外，不能觀察記者情況，「你知啲警察又唔識英文，如果雞同鴨講，驚對Suzanne不利。」她其後向在場PPRB警員理論，投訴撞跌她的警員，惟PPRB僅稱稍後跟進，Suzanne怒斥「I'm done」轉身離開。"},{"pid":"7c87066341636b7570ec02691fb5a535276fc280","tid":1630490,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e144a68aec73422db519081dec709098731b631d","tid":1630490,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec6af4efb0e793a0cda4267b70b4504d6c5b791a","tid":1630490,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"此外，防暴警又突然推撞戴綠色頭盔、穿反光衣的外媒女記者Suzanne Sataline，並將她包圍，嘗試制服她，但其後又釋放該名記者，未有解釋原因。Suzanne向記者表示，她在警方推進時跌倒，繼而有女示威者亦倒在她眼前，故她以電話繼續拍攝，惟遭警方不斷大叫「where are you from？」然而即使她多次回答來自美國，警方仍繼續追問，警方一時叫她離開、一時叫她坐下，令她感到無助，亦擔心其翻譯被捕；其間亦被警棍打到手部。<br />\n<br />\n幫Suzanne翻譯的劉先生指，Suzanne年屆56歲，在港採訪多年，剛才被警方推撞跌倒，被圍困時亦有警員朝她頭盔打一下。及後他被趕至10米範圍外，不能觀察記者情況，「你知啲警察又唔識英文，如果雞同鴨講，驚對Suzanne不利。」她其後向在場PPRB警員理論，投訴撞跌她的警員，惟PPRB僅稱稍後跟進，Suzanne怒斥「I'm done」轉身離開。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f961869668bf27b8a95dd90a82685ab500625fa5","tid":1630490,"uid":273670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"你知啲警察又唔識英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de81f170538f8a3d2f248138d4aadc81d63fa3c9","tid":1630490,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"煲大啦"},{"pid":"966b75b8613fc2fcc858cf5d3d9faebefffbc294","tid":1630490,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/bluegene20/status/1180793418332561409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbluegene20%2Fstatus%2F1180793418332561409&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6jizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=3b231009\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbluegene20%2Fstatus%2F1180793418332561409&h=14411cd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/bluegene20/status/1180793418332561409</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c8fc730547625cde8d46eff641b28107f22348","tid":1630490,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:54:56.000Z","msg":"毅進仔識撚America/USA點解咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424bc8aa0cac9d7ffbb079ccdb01650d9e8241c2","tid":1630490,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:56:49.000Z","msg"